## App Entry
- `cli/app.rs` — main CLI router + command dispatch
- `cli/mod.rs`

## Commands
- `cli/commands/`
  - `chat.rs` — interactive REPL / chat
  - `code.rs` — explain, review, generate, plan, test, fix
  - `config.rs`, `setup.rs`, `skills.rs`, `tools.rs`
  - `init.rs` — interactive project initialization
  - `bayes.rs`, `audit.rs`, `history.rs`, `health.rs`, `sandbox.rs`
  - `acp.rs`, `settings.rs`

## Interactive UI
- `display/` — banner, progress, workflow_viewer, interactive components
- `terminal/` — low-level terminal I/O

## Slash Commands (in ACP + chat)
- `/help`, `/clear`, `/context`, `/tools`, `/model`
- `/think off|low|high`
- `/goal <text>`, `/rule add|list|remove|clear`
- `/commit [instructions]`, `/bayes ...`, `/diagnostics`, `/visualize`

## Key Features
- Full command-line + interactive modes
- ACP server mode for Zed
- Rich display with workflow visualization

## Recent Changes
- Added many new CLI commands (`init`, `bayes`, `health`, `sandbox`)
- Improved slash command handling and goal/rule injection

## Dependencies
- `clap`, `inquire`, `crossterm`, `ratatui` (for some components)

## Notes
- CLI is the primary user interface.
- Many commands delegate to the engine / agent system.